The paper discusses the challenges of analyzing textual data, which is a common topic in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also addresses performance and scaling issues, which are relevant to the Database (cs.DB) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper proposes a new architecture for text analysis, which involves integrating various preprocessing techniques, which is a topic in the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
